    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty has been pampered since day one and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a single scratch or speck of dust anywhere! It\u2019s been garage-kept, meticulously maintained, and drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels and looks practically brand new, you\u2019ve found it. Come see it for yourself, you\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
