      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm honestly so excited to show you this absolute gem. It\u2019s been my pride and joy and is in truly pristine condition\u2014seriously, it still looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've taken such good care of it, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for a new adventure, you\u2019ve found it. Drop me a message, I'd love to chat more about it!",
      "price": 43900.0,
