    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the high-revving S54 platform. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six features individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing, delivering a linear power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed via a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and transmitted through a variable M differential lock. The chassis is structurally immaculate, with a documented subframe reinforcement and fresh bushings throughout the multi-link rear suspension. The cooling system has been overhauled with an aluminum radiator and high-flow water pump to ensure thermal efficiency under load. This vehicle retains factory-spec compression across all cylinders and exhibits zero oil consumption, representing a turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
